  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency markdown-it-anchor to v4",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor\">markdown-it-anchor</a> from <code>v2.7.1</code> to <code>v4.0.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"400\">4.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/4062d08dd67eb83d2e41d5269bddba51c51d601c\"><code>4062d08</code></a> Bump 4.0.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/2c97dd4384727af3b74a3e18380c5ab20bc6c991\"><code>2c97dd4</code></a> Support individual header level selection.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/8aecd75a44e7348ff1c601ede0e080db989507ed\"><code>8aecd75</code></a> Support code in titles</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/6483838cb6c400cd1b3039f9860583188344076d\"><code>6483838</code></a> Update dependencies, remove Babel</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/092a146dbdea722628c907249160e4ce7ccfcfbe\"><code>092a146</code></a> Fix readme example</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/56442a67b08953ff366f1b5e390652eb396a1ed3\"><code>56442a6</code></a> Update changelog</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"300\">3.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/valeriangalliat/markdown-it-anchor/commit/b0110e33d5aac43f0911ae798d02f1af2a4c709d\"><code>b0110e3</code></a> Bump 3.0.0</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
